{"tid":955404,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)聖誕特別節目","createTime":"2018-12-25T11:24:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T18:49:26.000Z","uid":29160,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e4030312bb6936bdd87271f61cc6137d969f04cd","tid":955404,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T11:24:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=nwIIHGTlHaa4WJpxqbIjP10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=16304c91\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=nwIIHGTlHaa4WJpxqbIjP10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=800f0108\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=nwIIHGTlHaa4WJpxqbIjP10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=ed341a95\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/4/47/Home_alone.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F4%2F47%2FHome_alone.jpg&h=865d659c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/c/cf/Krampus_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fc%2Fcf%2FKrampus_Poster.jpg&h=c4abe94e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://www.dramaqueen.com.tw/images/video_poster/2018/2018101214211820984aea26ce859b99d6ddec737f8ce8d92f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dramaqueen.com.tw%2Fimages%2Fvideo_poster%2F2018%2F2018101214211820984aea26ce859b99d6ddec737f8ce8d92f.jpg&h=ac9fbd17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.講述在聖誕節,主角和他的家人到巴黎探望他們的親人,卻出發前,主角卻被家人忘記了,被留在家中獨自用機智對付兩個小偷的故事。影片主要的拍攝地點在芝加哥。<br />\n<br />\n2.清晨，全家人又因為起晚了而匆匆拎上行李、慌忙地趕往機場。這一次，他們沒有把小凱文落下，但在機場混亂的人群中，凱文誤把別人當成了父親，跟著他登上了開往紐約的飛機，當他走下飛機後才恍然大悟，不過他可並不打算為此而傷心，相反凱文暗自慶幸著終於能自由自在地過聖誕節了。第一次來到這個完全陌生的大城市，聰明機靈的凱文也不禁暗暗害怕<br />\n<br />\n3.故事敘述一個不為人熟知的暗黑版聖誕節傳說,徹底顛覆我們對歡樂假期的想像。從小在衝突不斷的家庭中長大，年輕的麥斯對聖誕節早已不抱任何期望。但他一點也不知道，這種缺乏歡樂節日的精神已經燃起坎卜斯的憤怒，喚醒這一位古老的邪惡妖怪來懲罰不相信聖誕節的人們。當家喻戶曉的節慶主角化身成為惡魔開始攻擊這個破碎的家庭，迫使他們挺身為家人戰鬥，如果他們希望活下去...<br />\n<br />\n4.聖誕節當天，小女孩凱特在回味過往家人拍攝的影片時，意外發現疑似聖誕老人現身的蛛絲馬跡，遂與兄長泰迪合作守夜，打算用攝影機捕捉聖誕老人蒞臨的畫面。當晚兩人的守候也沒有落空，凱特與泰迪甚至還進一步偷溜上了聖誕老人的雪橇，卻因此使聖誕老人受到驚嚇，導致雪橇出了事故，使無數的孩子即將面臨收不到禮物的危機。闖禍的兄妹倆便與聖誕老人合作，攜手挽救聖誕節<br />\n<br />\n7 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聖誕快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=nwIIHGTlHaa4WJpxqbIjP10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=f3e1019d\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=nwIIHGTlHaa4WJpxqbIjP10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=45d87b20\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0483504cfa1616517e4653d3be4093149f074c1","tid":955404,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T11:32:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"800e02afab64ec7d0d86b873a2ef158ea112c216","tid":955404,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T12:36:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b74f5bcc36b3a6d83b6df25f604853017389fd4f","tid":955404,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T13:09:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b58d85489bf65fb40e40db7ea2db1651627d450","tid":955404,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T13:40:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7159c057a2cc39dbe61ce50e2a64d333a496f92","tid":955404,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T14:18:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dcb4d27b39a2a52d796c8809b6f5a18a22f6726","tid":955404,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T16:22:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"179738a86d58f0e709735bc2c52acab7e85645d1","tid":955404,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T16:50:59.000Z","msg"